# Next.js Rules

Prefer:

- Server Components
- Server Actions
- Route Handlers

Use Client Components only when required:

- state
- browser APIs
- event handlers

Avoid unnecessary "use client".

Keep layouts thin.

Keep pages simple.

Move reusable logic into lib/.